      <a href="/cook/japchae-recipe" class="related-card"><div class="related-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="related-card-pillar">Cook &middot; Side</div><div class="related-card-title">Japchae: Glass Noodles Done Right</div><div class="related-card-excerpt">The secret is cooking each vegetable separately.</div><div class="related-card-meta">Mar 5, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/cook/tteokbokki-recipe" class="related-card"><div class="related-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="related-card-pillar">Cook &middot; Snack</div><div class="related-card-title">Tteokbokki: Spicy Rice Cakes in 15 Minutes</div><div class="related-card-excerpt">Chewy, spicy, and ridiculously easy.</div><div class="related-card-meta">Feb 28, 2026</div></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

